---

<section id="nosotros" class="section-padding">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-collage">
        <div class="collage-inner">
          <figure class="collage-card collage-card-main">
            <img
              src="/galeria/about/barbero-franco.png"
              alt="Franco Santillan, barbero"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </figure>
          <figure class="collage-card collage-card-certificate">
            <img
              src="/galeria/certificado/certificado1.png"
              alt="Certificado de master class de barberia"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </figure>
          <figure class="collage-card collage-card-tools">
            <img
              src="/galeria/maquinas/maquinas1.jpeg"
              alt="Maquinas y herramientas de barberia"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <div class="gold-label">SOBRE NOSOTROS</div>
        <h2 class="about-heading">El mejor corte para cada cliente.</h2>
        <p class="about-body">
          Trabajo desde casa, en Moreno, siempre busco que cada cliente
          salga sintiéndose bien. Sin apuros, sin mal trabajo.
        </p>
        <p class="about-body">
          Empecé cortando en el barrio y crecí de boca en boca. Hoy tengo
          clientes fijos que vienen hace años — eso dice más que cualquier
          publicidad.
        </p>
        <p class="about-body">
          Cada corte es personal. Me tomo el tiempo de entender qué querés y
          cómo lo podés mantener.
        </p>
        <ul class="about-checkmarks">
          <li>Años de experiencia</li><li>Garantía de calidad</li><li>
            Barbero certificado
          </li><li>100% personalizado</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="#certificacion" class="btn btn-ghost">LEER MÁS →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  #nosotros {
    background: var(--bg);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .about-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 40px;
  }
  .about-text {
    order: 1;
  }
  .about-collage {
    order: 2;
  }
  .about-heading {
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 6vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1.2;
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .about-heading::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 60px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--gold);
  }
  .about-body {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .about-checkmarks {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px 24px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }
  .about-checkmarks li {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  .about-checkmarks li::before {
    content: "✓";
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-right: 6px;
  }
  .collage-inner {
    --card-bg: #111;
    --photo-border: rgba(240, 236, 228, 0.1);
    --photo-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
    isolation: isolate;
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: clamp(520px, 42vw, 710px);
    overflow: visible;
  }
  .collage-inner::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 7% 6% 4% 11%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.22);
    transform: rotate(-1.8deg);
    z-index: -1;
  }
  .collage-card {
    position: absolute;
    margin: 0;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--photo-border);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 52px var(--photo-shadow);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .collage-card::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.18);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .collage-card img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .collage-card-main {
    left: 4%;
    top: 2%;
    width: 48%;
    height: 92%;
    z-index: 1;
    transform: rotate(-2deg);
  }
  .collage-card-main img {
    object-position: 82% center;
  }
  .collage-card-main::after {
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      rgba(8, 8, 8, 0.96) 0%,
      rgba(8, 8, 8, 0.72) 24%,
      rgba(8, 8, 8, 0.14) 54%,
      transparent 72%
    );
  }
  .collage-card-certificate {
    right: 0;
    top: 4%;
    width: 53%;
    height: 34%;
    z-index: 3;
    padding: 14px;
    background:
      linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), transparent 36%),
      #101010;
    transform: rotate(1.5deg);
  }
  .collage-card-certificate img {
    object-fit: contain;
  }
  .collage-card-tools {
    right: 2%;
    bottom: 4%;
    width: 48%;
    height: 53%;
    z-index: 2;
    transform: rotate(1deg);
  }
  .collage-card-tools img {
    object-position: 52% 42%;
  }
  .collage-card-main::before,
  .collage-card-certificate::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 0;
    width: 72px;
    height: 18px;
    background: rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.48);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
    transform: translate(-50%, -45%) rotate(-3deg);
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .collage-card-certificate::before {
    left: 22%;
    width: 58px;
    transform: translate(-50%, -45%) rotate(4deg);
  }
  @media (hover: hover) {
    .collage-card {
      transition:
        transform 0.45s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1),
        box-shadow 0.45s ease;
    }
    .collage-card-main:hover {
      transform: rotate(-1deg) translateY(-6px);
    }
    .collage-card-certificate:hover {
      transform: rotate(0.5deg) translateY(-6px);
    }
    .collage-card-tools:hover {
      transform: rotate(0deg) translateY(-6px);
    }
    .collage-card:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 30px 68px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .about-collage {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .collage-inner {
      height: clamp(440px, 125vw, 620px);
      max-width: 520px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .collage-inner::before {
      inset: 8% 4% 2% 8%;
    }
    .collage-card-main {
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      width: 72%;
      height: 78%;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .collage-card-certificate {
      right: 2%;
      top: 47%;
      bottom: auto;
      width: 62%;
      height: 23%;
      padding: 9px;
      z-index: 4;
      transform: rotate(-1deg);
    }
    .collage-card-tools {
      right: 0;
      top: 63%;
      bottom: auto;
      width: 58%;
      height: 35%;
      z-index: 3;
      transform: rotate(2deg);
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 420px) {
    .collage-inner {
      height: 420px;
    }
    .collage-card-main {
      width: 72%;
    }
    .collage-card-certificate {
      top: 47%;
      width: 64%;
      height: 21%;
      padding: 7px;
    }
    .collage-card-tools {
      top: 62%;
      width: 58%;
      height: 35%;
    }
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 60px;
    }
    .about-text {
      flex: 1;
      order: 0;
    }
    .about-collage {
      flex: 1;
      order: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
